data.description: This is an absolute gem, in this great neighborhood in Bullard!   Featuring an oversized lot and 3-car garage!   The home is located in the heart of Bullard, literally minutes from Brook Hill and Bullard Schools.  Enjoy the large covered patio while watching the family play in the pool in the summer.  The large kitchen has an expansive island, 42 in. cabinets, an abundance of storage and opens into the living room and dining area.   The living room has lovely crown molding and 6.5-inch baseboards. The primary bedroom boasts a tray ceiling and crown molding. This home has recessed lighting in the living and kitchen areas, a tankless water heater and a central vac!   The utility room has enough space for a small freezer.  Contact me today to tour this charming home!
